{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cf8914036b","title":"给谢觉截的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"29d381eedf","index":0,"year":1941,"month":8,"day":12,"articleId":"cf8914036b"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji16","name":"毛泽东全集第16卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji16.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji16":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e86193a18e","type":"paragraph","text":"给谢觉截的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"cf8914036b"},{"id":"5e96e279a6","type":"paragraph","text":"（1941年8月12日）谢老：十一日信悉。劳役须经政治动员是完全对的，这就是我们的劳役与国民党的劳役之原则的区别，我们的特点是革命加战争。边府党团不应与政府委员会混同，党团只须三、五人，任务是掌握政策，有事即谈，谈通了，或拟成了计划，商得西北局同意（或常委通过）就提在政府委员会上通过。党团会由你召集，也不必各厅都有人，以能考虑政策的人为限。此事请考虑。创主席问题可考虑敬礼！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"cf8914036b"},{"id":"21f1937b98","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"cf8914036b"},{"id":"c820b44be3","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十二日[1]指肤甘宁边区政府党团。党团，当时是中国共产党在政府、工会、绘及共他群众组织中建立的党的领导机构。在中国共产党第七次全国代表","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"cf8914036b"}],"page":{"id":"5780f5d6b6","publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"cf8914036b","start":197,"end":197}}}},"__N_SSG":true}